{"data":[{"author":"Amicisoft","capabilities":["location","configurable"],"category_id":"5261a8fb3b773043d500000f","category_name":"Tools & Utilities","category_color":"fdbf37","changelog":[{"version":"0.2","published_date":"2016-03-08T04:49:59.095Z","release_notes":"Increased max distance to 5000 km/3000 miles"},{"version":"0.1","published_date":"2016-02-28T18:44:27.862Z","release_notes":"First beta release"}],"companions":{"ios":null,"android":null},"compatibility":{"ios":{"supported":true,"min_js_version":-1},"android":{"supported":true},"aplite":{"supported":true,"firmware":{"major":3}},"basalt":{"supported":true,"firmware":{"major":3}},"chalk":{"supported":true,"firmware":{"major":3}},"diorite":{"supported":true,"firmware":{"major":3}},"emery":{"supported":true,"firmware":{"major":3}}},"created_at":"2016-02-28T08:19:03.364Z","description":"Track your friends and family using Amicudar, a radar display on your wrist! Personalize with one of the included avatars and create a geofence to be notified when others are nearby.\r\n\r\nSETUP\r\n1) Install Amicudar.\r\n2) Open Settings on your phone and enter a user and group name.\r\n3) Send your friends and family your group name.\r\n\r\nThen use Amicudar's menu system to choose an avatar, select metric/imperial, define a geofence, select an update interval, and show/hide the time.\r\n\r\nUSAGE\r\n• The up/down buttons zoom in/out\r\n• Shake to activate the display for 1 minute. The compass will show your actual heading and the progress bar will countdown to the next update.\r\n• Joining and leaving the group is as simple as opening and closing Amicudar. You'll automatically be removed from the group after a little while once you switch to a watchface or another app.\r\n• The status bar turns red if an update fails.\r\n\r\nWe're currently in beta and we would appreciate your feedback!","developer_id":"56d2551ffc2d703a5d00004f","header_images":[{"orig":"https://assets.getpebble.com/api/file/OansQksZRHalleAVMg5G/convert?c